SIMPLE: dissected
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dissected
<hw>Dis*sect"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Cut
into several parts; divided into sections; <as>as, a <ex>dissected</ex>
map</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Cut deeply into many lobes or
divisions; <as>as, a <ex>dissected</ex> leaf</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dissectible</ent>⟦br⟧
